55:44.506 --> 55:45.571
    <i> NORA: "Dear Miss Hanff.</i>

55:45.573 --> 55:47.539
   <i> "For a long time,</i>
   <i> I've wanted to write to you</i>

55:47.541 --> 55:51.509
 <i> "to thank you</i>
 <i> for my family's share</i>
 <i> in the wonderful food parcels</i>

55:51.511 --> 55:55.513
       <i> "you've been sending</i>
       <i> to Marks & Co."</i>

55:55.781 --> 55:58.882
      Five minutes later
      we'd have been soaked.

55:58.884 --> 56:01.384
      <i> "Now I have an excuse,</i>
      <i> as Frank tells me</i>

56:01.386 --> 56:05.054
      <i> "you want to know</i>
      <i> the name and address</i>
      <i> of the old lady</i>

56:05.056 --> 56:07.623
  <i> "who embroidered your cloth.</i>

56:07.625 --> 56:14.096
   <i> "Her name is Mrs. Boulton</i>
   <i> and she lives upstairs</i>
   <i> at No. 24 Oakfield Court.</i>

56:14.098 --> 56:17.732
   <i> "She was thrilled</i>
   <i> to know her cloth</i>
   <i> had crossed the Atlantic.</i>

56:17.734 --> 56:22.703
   <i> "And I know,</i>
   <i> she'd be delighted to hear</i>
   <i> how much you admired it.</i>

56:23.972 --> 56:28.174
  <i> "I thought you might like to</i>
  <i> see these snaps</i>
  <i> of my happy family.</i>

56:28.176 --> 56:32.011
      <i> "Our eldest girl</i>
      <i> was 12 last August,</i>
      <i> by name Sheila,</i>

56:32.013 --> 56:34.613
    <i> "who, by the way,</i>
    <i> is my ready-made daughter,</i>

56:34.615 --> 56:37.849
  <i> "as Frank lost his first wife</i>
  <i> during the war.</i>

56:37.851 --> 56:41.719
       <i> "Our youngest, Mary,</i>
       <i> was 4 last week.</i>

56:41.721 --> 56:44.154
    <i> "Last May,</i>
    <i> Sheila announced at school</i>

56:44.156 --> 56:47.557
      <i> "she was sending</i>
      <i> Mummy and Daddy</i>
      <i> an anniversary card</i>

56:47.559 --> 56:49.959
        <i> "and told the nuns,</i>
        <i> it's a convent,</i>

56:49.961 --> 56:52.761
      <i> "that we had been married</i>
      <i> four years!</i>

56:52.763 --> 56:53.428
          <i> (NORA LAUGHS)</i>

56:53.430 --> 56:56.464
  <i> "It took a bit of explaining,</i>
  <i> as you can imagine.</i>

56:56.466 --> 56:59.233
        <i> "I will close this</i>
        <i> with all good wishes</i>
        <i> for the new year</i>

56:59.235 --> 57:04.104
 <i> "and a special wish</i>
 <i> that we may see you</i>
 <i> in England one of these days.</i>

57:04.439 --> 57:07.373
      <i> "Sincerely, Nora Doel."</i>

